<p>A large police operation in Rio de Janeiro’s favelas left the death toll at 132, state authorities said, in what local media called the deadliest police action in the state’s history . Authorities said the raid aimed to capture leaders and curb the territorial expansion of the Red Command gang, a long‑standing drug trafficking group in Rio&#x27;s poor neighborhoods . The operation has provoked strong reactions: families began burying victims, residents are divided over the tactics used, and international voices including the U.N. have called for an independent investigation amid condemnation from human rights organisations .</p><img src='https://kagiproxy.com/img/136yYXvSzMRJCl8U_Zw2uB8Si4YVVUDL6RJLiJvT0W-dgVifM-QqhXsP-EhdNLPeu86ccRRM3R4-Segc-0L-K5-RPxeq5_bsAzfgvv2eMmbSdaCtL6d0y13iXJeGX3vy4-Tz1lER9gf-bbUEHtuujzFywPmFNMgFnk9xg8b-L4SFq4zL09LCYYepT5gQhcPXRRUrhLITDKgCK6W8' alt='The bodies of people killed during the raid.' /><br /><h3>Highlights:</h3><ul><li>Police casualties: Officials reported that among those killed were multiple police officers, with at least four police fatalities cited in some accounts .</li><li>Governor&#x27;s role: The operation was ordered by Rio state governor Claudio Castro, a 46‑year‑old conservative who oversees the state&#x27;s police forces .</li><li>Local division: Residents in affected neighborhoods expressed split views—some praised the action while others accused authorities of excessive force .</li><li>Community impact: Families in the favelas have begun burying victims and communities are grappling with shock and demands for answers .</li></ul><h3>Perspectives:</h3><ul><li>Rio state authorities: Officials defended the operation as necessary to capture gang leaders and limit the territorial expansion of the Red Command. (<a href='http://www.euronews.com/2025/10/31/angry-families-begin-burying-dead-after-police-raid-on-rio-favela-kills-at-least-132'>Euronews</a>)</li><li>Governor Claudio Castro: The raid was ordered under the governor&#x27;s office as part of a security push overseen by his administration. (<a href='https://www.lemonde.fr/en/international/article/2025/10/31/rio-de-janeiro-claudio-castro-the-governor-behind-the-deadliest-police-raid-in-the-state-s-history_6746944_4.html'>Le Monde</a>)</li><li>Favela residents and families: Many families are burying the dead and community members say they are reeling and demanding explanations. (<a href='https://abcnews.go.com/International/wireStory/rio-favelas-left-reeling-after-lethal-gang-raid-127047508'>ABC News</a>)</li><li>United Nations: The U.N. has called for an independent investigation into the operation. (<a href='https://www.france24.com/en/video/20251031-rio-residents-divided-over-the-deadly-historic-raid-against-drug-gang'>France 24</a>)</li><li>Human rights organisations: Several human rights groups condemned the raid and urged accountability and transparent probes. (<a href='https://www.straitstimes.com/world/calls-for-tougher-stance-on-gangs-grow-in-brazil-after-deadly-rio-raid'>The Straits Times</a>)</li></ul><h3>Sources:</h3><ul><li><a href='https://www.nytimes.com/2025/10/29/world/americas/rio-brazil-police-raid-deaths.html'>Police Raid in Rio de Janeiro Leaves Over 130 Dead</a> - nytimes.com</li><li><a href='http://www.euronews.com/2025/10/31/angry-families-begin-burying-dead-after-police-raid-on-rio-favela-kills-at-least-132'>Angry families begin burying dead after police raid on Rio favela kills at least 132</a> - euronews.com</li><li><a href='https://www.france24.com/en/video/20251031-rio-residents-divided-over-the-deadly-historic-raid-against-drug-gang'>Rio residents divided over the deadly historic raid against drug gang</a> - france24.com</li><li><a href='https://www.straitstimes.com/world/calls-for-tougher-stance-on-gangs-grow-in-brazil-after-deadly-rio-raid'>Calls for tougher stance on gangs grow in Brazil after deadly Rio raid</a> - straitstimes.com</li><li><a href='https://abcnews.go.com/International/wireStory/rio-favelas-left-reeling-after-lethal-gang-raid-127047508'>Rio favelas left reeling after lethal gang raid as families bury the dead</a> - abcnews.go.com</li><li><a href='https://www.lemonde.fr/en/international/article/2025/10/31/rio-de-janeiro-claudio-castro-the-governor-behind-the-deadliest-police-raid-in-the-state-s-history_6746944_4.html'>Claudio Castro, the Brazilian governor behind the deadliest police raid in Rio de Janeiro&#x27;s history</a> - lemonde.fr</li></ul>